description:
• What we'll do
Tune in and watch the Google I/O keynote and enjoy conversation, food and drinks with fellow SWmobile members.

The keynote starts at 6:00pm which is an hour earlier than our Meetups usually start.

We're kindly being hosted by Dyson in their new office just off College Green. See the event photo for where to find the door.

• Important to know
Venue security requirements means we need to have full names of all attendees, so each attendee will need to register separately rather than as '+1's.

RSVPs will close on the Friday 3rd at 4pm as Monday is a Bank Holiday.
title: Google I/O 2019 - Keynote
